Avon - ON - iOS App

COMPONENT
Notifications

ACTION PERFORMED
1. Launch Avon On
2. Navigates to SSH - scheduled posts (Tervezett posztok)
3. Choose 1 schedule post with (...) in the right top corner
4. Select the option "schedule" (Szerkesztés)
5. Press the button Következő
6. In the menu select Allits be emlekeztetot
7. Select time (For example, 21.14) and tap on beallitva
8. When notifications will come tap on the pop-up message

EXPECTED RESULT
The app should keep work

ACTUAL RESULT
The app crashes after tapping the pop-up notifications

DEVICE AND OS 
iPhone 8 iOS 14.0.1

Country 
Hungary
